  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2996000/extras/0b72bcb472d36c8ebaa7b6f881ef00c9.poster.avif?t=1750909860\" width=600 height=231 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2996000/extras/0b72bcb472d36c8ebaa7b6f881ef00c9.webm?t=1750909860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build machines, establish power grids, and expand territory. Upgrade from hands-on crafting to high-tech automated production, evolving from raw wood to cutting-edge warp coils. Continuously enhance technology, scale operations, and coordinate specialized robots for manufacturing, resource gathering, and agriculture. Leverage the global management system to maximize efficiency and drive production to its peak.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2996000/extras/9eeda757daca94f5b68d3b5ed098e1bf.poster.avif?t=1750909860\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2996000/extras/9eeda757daca94f5b68d3b5ed098e1bf.webm?t=1750909860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Settle into the rhythm of tranquil island life by tending crops, gathering resources, preparing meals, and fishing amid the calm. Roam the island to discover a variety of animals, some of which may become loyal companions with the right gift. Unlock plant gene enhancements, push technological boundaries, and direct the evolution of helpful robots. Harness creativity to build medical pods and restore the damaged ship.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2996000/extras/1fa4d699849aadc2a628cccc9bcc1ed8.poster.avif?t=1750909860\" width=600 height=231 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2996000/extras/1fa4d699849aadc2a628cccc9bcc1ed8.webm?t=1750909860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Engage in strategic real-time tower defense challenges. Deploy a variety of unique towers and utilize the island’s diverse terrains like jungles, deserts, canyons, and labyrinths for effective defenses. Battle alien creatures hidden throughout the wilderness in fast-paced encounters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2996000/extras/b26aa3fbc6e55f5c4bdd7a743b1a3b2c.poster.avif?t=1750909860\" width=600 height=231 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2996000/extras/b26aa3fbc6e55f5c4bdd7a743b1a3b2c.webm?t=1750909860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a town filled with devout followers, elusive monsters, cryptic notes, eerie underground chambers, and blood-stained rituals, each contributing to a hidden narrative. As clues are pieced together, a shadowy past begins to surface, revealing the island’s most guarded and unsettling mysteries.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2996000/extras/0b72bcb472d36c8ebaa7b6f881ef00c9.poster.avif?t=1750909860\" width=600 height=231 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2996000/extras/0b72bcb472d36c8ebaa7b6f881ef00c9.webm?t=1750909860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build machines, establish power grids, and expand territory. Upgrade from hands-on crafting to high-tech automated production, evolving from raw wood to cutting-edge warp coils. Continuously enhance technology, scale operations, and coordinate specialized robots for manufacturing, resource gathering, and agriculture. Leverage the global management system to maximize efficiency and drive production to its peak.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2996000/extras/9eeda757daca94f5b68d3b5ed098e1bf.poster.avif?t=1750909860\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2996000/extras/9eeda757daca94f5b68d3b5ed098e1bf.webm?t=1750909860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Settle into the rhythm of tranquil island life by tending crops, gathering resources, preparing meals, and fishing amid the calm. Roam the island to discover a variety of animals, some of which may become loyal companions with the right gift. Unlock plant gene enhancements, push technological boundaries, and direct the evolution of helpful robots. Harness creativity to build medical pods and restore the damaged ship.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class